---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import historiaData from '../content/pages/es/historia.json';
---

<Layout title="Historia" currentPage="historia">
  <!-- BLOQUE 1: Historia Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-racing"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
      <div class="absolute top-1/4 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-racing-green rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <span class="text-vanilla text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 block">Grip Club</span>
          <h1 class="section-title mb-8">
            Nuestra <span class="text-vanilla">Historia</span>
          </h1>
        </div>

        <!-- Two Column Layout: Text Left, Images Right -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <!-- Left Column: Text -->
          <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
            <p class="text-racing-silver text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Grip Club nació de una pasión compartida por el motorsport.
              Un grupo de amigos, entusiastas de las motos, que querían crear algo diferente: una competición accesible, emocionante y capaz de reunir a la comunidad motera en torno a un evento único.
            </p>
            <p class="text-racing-silver text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Desde el primer momento tuvimos claro el formato. Inspirados por los grandes campeonatos internacionales de resistencia, adaptamos el concepto a nuestro país manteniendo su esencia más pura: motos 125cc de serie, pilotos amateur y desafíos en circuito donde el equipo y el piloto importa más que la propia moto.
            </p>
            <p class="text-racing-silver text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Pero Grip Club no nace solo de una idea feliz. Nace de muchos años viviendo los circuitos desde dentro: organizando carreras de resistencia, trackdays y encuentros que han reunido a miles de apasionados del motor. Proyectos como las 24H Experiences, Trackdays con 8000vueltas o eventos de cultura del motor como Autopía nos han dado algo que no se improvisa: experiencia real, criterio y una obsesión por hacer las cosas bien.
            </p>
            <p class="text-racing-silver text-lg leading-relaxed">
              Todo ese bagaje es el que hoy se canaliza en Grip Club. Lo que empezó como una idea entre amigos se ha convertido en una realidad pensada para equipos y pilotos de toda España, con un objetivo claro: ofrecer una experiencia accesible, auténtica y cuidada al detalle, donde cada persona que entra al box, sale a pista o vive el paddock sienta que forma parte de algo especial.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Right Column: Images -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-racing-silver/20">
              <img
                src="https://placehold.co/800x500/1a1a1a/00ff88?text=Motorsport+Passion"
                alt="Historia Grip Club"
                class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-racing-silver/20">
                <img
                  src="https://placehold.co/400x300/1a1a1a/00ff88?text=Racing+Spirit"
                  alt="Racing Spirit"
                  class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
                  loading="lazy"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-racing-silver/20">
                <img
                  src="https://placehold.co/400x300/1a1a1a/00ff88?text=Team+Work"
                  alt="Team Work"
                  class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
                  loading="lazy"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BLOQUE 2: Los Tres Pilares - Core Concepts -->
  {historiaData.threePillars && (
    <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-racing-black relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-racing-green rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-racing-green rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 relative z-10">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <span class="text-racing-green text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 block">{historiaData.conceptoTagline}</span>
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
              {historiaData.conceptoTitle} <span class="text-vanilla">{historiaData.conceptoTitleAccent}</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-racing-silver text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto">
              Tres conceptos fundamentales que definen nuestra filosofía y hacen que GRIP Club sea diferente.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-16 md:space-y-24">
            {historiaData.threePillars.map((pillar, index) => (
              <div class={`grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center ${index % 2 === 1 ? 'lg:flex-row-reverse' : ''}`}>
                <div class={`${index % 2 === 1 ? 'lg:order-2' : ''}`}>
                  <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-racing-green/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                      {pillar.icon === 'motorcycle' && (
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-racing-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
                        </svg>
                      )}
                      {pillar.icon === 'stopwatch' && (
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-racing-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                        </svg>
                      )}
                      {pillar.icon === 'users' && (
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-racing-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
                        </svg>
                      )}
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-vanilla" style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">
                        {pillar.headline}
                      </h3>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <p class="text-racing-green font-semibold text-lg mb-4">{pillar.subheadline}</p>

                  <p class="text-racing-silver text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    {pillar.description}
                  </p>

                  <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
                    {pillar.bullets.map((bullet) => (
                      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-racing-green flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="text-white text-base">{bullet}</span>
                      </li>
                    ))}
                  </ul>
                </div>

                <div class={`${index % 2 === 1 ? 'lg:order-1' : ''}`}>
                  <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-racing-silver/20 group">
                    <img
                      src={`https://placehold.co/800x600/1a1a1a/00ff88?text=${pillar.id}`}
                      alt={pillar.headline}
                      class="w-full h-auto object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105"
                      loading="lazy"
                    />
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-racing-black/80 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  )}

  <!-- BLOQUE 3: Vision, Mision, Valores - Compact Design -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-racing-black">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">

        <!-- Vision -->
        <div class="mb-10">
          <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <span class="text-vanilla text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 block">Por qué 125cc</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">Las ventajas del <span class="text-vanilla">formato</span></h2>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
            {historiaData.conceptCards.map((card) => (
              <div class="card-compact group">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-racing-green/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:bg-racing-green/30 transition-colors">
                    {card.icon === 'money' && (
                      <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-vanilla" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                      </svg>
                    )}
                    {card.icon === 'lightning' && (
                      <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-vanilla" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"/>
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
                      </svg>
                    )}
                    {card.icon === 'team' && (
                      <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-vanilla" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
                      </svg>
                    )}
                    {card.icon === 'shield' && (
                      <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-vanilla" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"/>
                      </svg>
                    )}
                    {card.icon === 'book' && (
                      <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-vanilla" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/>
                      </svg>
                    )}
                    {card.icon === 'smile' && (
                      <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-vanilla" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                      </svg>
                    )}
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex-1">
                    <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-white mb-1.5">{card.title}</h3>
                    <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm leading-snug">{card.description}</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-racing-silver/20 my-10"></div>

        <!-- Mision -->
        <div class="mb-10">
          <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <span class="text-vanilla text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 block">Misión</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">Espíritu de <span class="text-vanilla">Equipo</span></h2>
          </div>
          <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-center">
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <p class="text-racing-silver leading-relaxed">
                  Seréis de 4 a 8 pilotos por equipo, unidos por una misma moto y un mismo objetivo: resistir y llegar juntos hasta el final. Gestionar nervios, tráfico, repostajes y decisiones bajo presión.
                </p>
                <p class="text-racing-silver leading-relaxed">
                  Lo importante es vivir la resistencia con vuestros amigos: compartir nervios, risas, sustos y remontadas hasta la bandera a cuadros.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-racing-silver/20">
                  <img src="https://placehold.co/300x200/1a1a1a/00ff88?text=Team+Spirit" alt="Team Spirit" class="w-full h-auto object-cover" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-racing-silver/20">
                  <img src="https://placehold.co/300x200/1a1a1a/00ff88?text=Paddock" alt="Paddock" class="w-full h-auto object-cover" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-racing-silver/20 my-10"></div>

        <!-- Valores -->
        <div>
          <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <span class="text-vanilla text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 block">Valores</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">Lo que nos <span class="text-vanilla">define</span></h2>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <div class="card-compact text-center">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-racing-green/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-vanilla" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Comunidad</h3>
              <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm">Unidos por la pasión: motociclismo en su esencia, sin filtros.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-compact text-center">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-racing-green/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-vanilla" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Accesibilidad</h3>
              <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm">El motorsport no tiene que ser exclusivo. Todos pueden participar.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-compact text-center">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-racing-green/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-vanilla" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Seguridad</h3>
              <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm">Máxima prioridad: equipamiento obligatorio y controles técnicos.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BLOQUE 4: CTA - Se parte de nuestra historia -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-racing-gray">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="section-title mb-6">{historiaData.ctaTitle} <span class="text-vanilla">{historiaData.ctaTitleAccent}</span></h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle mx-auto mb-8">
          {historiaData.ctaSubtitle}
        </p>
        <a href="/inscripciones#registro" class="btn-primary">
          {historiaData.ctaButton}
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Compact Card Styles */
  .card-compact {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .card-compact:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-color: var(--racing-green);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  /* Responsive adjustments */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .card-compact {
      padding: 0.875rem;
    }
  }
</style>

